resources.string: Web Based Android Application: LSU Medical Dictionary was created by a team of experienced and trained IT students from La Salle University, Ozamis City who are passionate about developing a restorative lexicon with the goal of making it easier for the students to locate words in a faster and convenient way. We believe that everybody should have access to an application that will make them feel bringing a whole dictionary in their hands but without any hassle. Our expertise and commitment to excellence in creating this application ensures that you will experience the most satisfying way from our LSU Medical Dictionary.
